(Olivia) RETRACT THE DUCT
A LITTLE MORE LATERALLY.

31:03.562 --> 31:05.194
SUCTION.

31:05.194 --> 31:07.196
(man) ANYONE MAKE IT
TO GRAND ROUNDS TODAY?

31:07.196 --> 31:09.198
THIS GUY FROM YALE SAYS

31:09.198 --> 31:11.200
HE CAN ENHANCE MEMORY
OF THE FLASH-FORWARDS

31:11.200 --> 31:13.903
USING A CALCINEURIN ANTAGONIST.
YEAH, I WAS THERE.
PRETTY COOL.

31:13.903 --> 31:16.045
(man) YEAH.
IRRIGATION, PLEASE.

31:16.045 --> 31:18.978
(monitor beeping rapidly)

31:18.978 --> 31:20.649
(man) B.P.'s 78 OVER 54.

31:20.649 --> 31:24.153
STAY CLEAR
OF THE HEPATIC ARTERY.
800 CCs OUT.

31:24.153 --> 31:26.885
GUYS, SYSTOLIC'S IN FREEFALL.
MUST BE ANOTHER BLEEDER
SOMEWHERE.

31:26.885 --> 31:28.487
OR SOME KIND OF FLUID SHIFT.

31:28.487 --> 31:31.660
GET ANOTHER UNIT
ON THE RAPID INFUSER.
(man) TRIBUTARY'S LIGATED.

31:31.660 --> 31:33.562
(woman) RUN OF 6.
(Olivia) 100 OF LIDO RIGHT AWAY.

31:33.562 --> 31:35.664
(monitor emitting
continuous tone)
HE'S IN V-TAC.

31:35.664 --> 31:37.997
(man) NO PULSE.
DAMN IT. CODE CART AND A MIG
OF EPI. LET'S GO! LET'S GO!

31:37.997 --> 31:40.029
(man) LIDO'S IN.

31:40.029 --> 31:42.201
WHERE'S THE CART?
WHERE'S THE CART?!
(monitor emitting
continuous tone)

31:42.201 --> 31:45.334
(woman)
YOU'RE CHARGED FOR 360.

31:45.334 --> 31:47.136
(Olivia) CLEAR.
(paddles thunk)

31:47.136 --> 31:48.978
(monitor emitting
continuous tone)

31:48.978 --> 31:50.139
NO CHANGE.

31:50.139 --> 31:52.041
GOING AGAIN.

31:52.041 --> 31:53.542
CLEAR.

32:04.223 --> 32:08.057
(monitor emitting
continuous tone)

32:08.057 --> 32:11.600
(man) FOURTH EPI'S IN.
(Olivia) CHASE IT WITH LIDO.

32:11.600 --> 32:14.133
HE'S HAD FIVE ROUNDS.
AMIODARONE THEN.

32:14.133 --> 32:16.966
THIS MAKES NO SENSE.
THIS MAKES NO SENSE AT ALL.

32:16.966 --> 32:20.569
(woman) E.B.L.'s
HOLDING AROUND 850.
NO CARDIAC HISTORY.
BLEEDING'S CONTROLLED.

32:20.569 --> 32:23.112
THIS IS CRAZY.
I DON'T GET IT.

32:28.147 --> 32:31.150
100 MIGs OF HYDROCORTISONE.
I.V. PUSH.

32:31.150 --> 32:33.983
IT'S ADRENAL CRISIS.
HE'S GOT ADDISON'S DISEASE.

32:33.983 --> 32:36.025
WHAT? NOBODY BOTHERED
TO TELL ME THIS?

32:36.025 --> 32:39.358
HE HASN'T BEEN DIAGNOSED YET.
ADDISON'S WOULD EXPLAIN
THE LACK OF RESPONSE

32:39.358 --> 32:42.061
TO FLUIDS AND PRESSORS.
EXACTLY. HOLD COMPRESSIONS.

32:42.061 --> 32:45.134
HOLDING.

32:45.134 --> 32:48.137
(monitor emitting
continuous tone)

32:50.439 --> 32:53.572
(beeping steadily)

32:53.572 --> 32:57.106
NORMAL SINUS.

32:57.106 --> 33:00.249
GOOD CAROTID.
NICE CATCH, DR. BENFORD.

33:06.615 --> 33:09.458
LET'S CLOSE HIM UP.

33:15.364 --> 33:18.527
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT AGENT NOH'S MURDER?

33:18.527 --> 33:21.100
HIS MURDER?

33:21.100 --> 33:23.702
SOMETHING FUNNY
ABOUT THAT?

33:23.702 --> 33:27.106
JUST THAT I KNEW HE DIDN'T
HAVE A FLASH-FORWARD.

33:27.106 --> 33:29.408
I HAD NO IDEA
HE WAS GONNA BE MURDERED...

33:29.408 --> 33:33.042
TILL NOW.
THEN HOW DID YOU KNOW
HE DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING?

33:33.042 --> 33:35.514
BECAUSE YOUR PARTNER
POSTED IT ON THE INTERNET,

33:35.514 --> 33:38.016
BECAUSE EVERYONE
IN THIS OFFICE KNOWS.

33:38.016 --> 33:41.050
ANY PARTICULAR REASON WHY YOU
FELT THE NEED TO WASTE THE TIME

33:41.050 --> 33:43.052
OF THE AGENTS INVESTIGATING
THE BLACKOUT?

33:43.052 --> 33:46.295
IN ALL LIKELIHOOD, NOTHING
I TELL YOU WILL BE THE TRUTH.

33:46.295 --> 33:48.697
SO WHY PERSIST IN ASKING?

33:48.697 --> 33:51.060
ASKING QUESTIONS IS MY JOB.

33:51.060 --> 33:55.164
SO LET'S START
WITH A SIMPLE ONE.

33:55.164 --> 33:57.035
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT THE BLACKOUT?

33:57.035 --> 34:00.109
THAT'S NOT
A SIMPLE QUESTION.

34:00.109 --> 34:01.670
ALL RIGHT.

34:01.670 --> 34:04.173
YOU EVER BEEN TO SOMALIA?

34:04.173 --> 34:07.045
I CAN'T SAY
I'VE HAD THE PLEASURE.

34:07.045 --> 34:09.218
WHAT ABOUT DETROIT?

34:09.218 --> 34:11.420
UTAH?

34:11.420 --> 34:15.154
YOU'RE WASTING YOUR ENERGY
ON WHAT CAUSED THE BLACKOUT,

34:15.154 --> 34:17.126
WHO'S RESPONSIBLE.

34:17.126 --> 34:20.789
YOU'RE IGNORING THE MOST
PROFOUND QUESTION OF ALL...

34:20.789 --> 34:24.263
WHY?

34:24.263 --> 34:26.635
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT A BLACK SWAN IS?

34:28.537 --> 34:32.771
IT'S A METAPHOR USED TO DESCRIBE
A HIGH-IMPACT EVENT...

34:32.771 --> 34:36.074
SOMETHING SO RARE
IT'S BEYOND THE NORMAL REALM

34:36.074 --> 34:37.806
OF HUMAN EXPECTATION.

34:37.806 --> 34:41.850
IT COMES FROM THE 17th CENTURY
WHEN SCIENTISTS ASSUMED

34:41.850 --> 34:44.583
THAT ALL SWANS WERE WHITE.
THEY WERE WRONG.

34:44.583 --> 34:46.555
FASCINATING.

34:46.555 --> 34:51.760
(speaks Farsi)

34:51.760 --> 34:58.267
"THERE'S A ROOM. A SMALL BOY
ENTERS WITH A CANDLE."

34:58.267 --> 34:59.798
WHAT IS THIS,
A BEDTIME STORY?

34:59.798 --> 35:01.600
IT'S A SUFI PARABLE.

35:01.600 --> 35:04.133
THE MAN IN THE ROOM,
REFERRING TO THE CANDLE,

35:04.133 --> 35:07.136
ASKS, "TELL ME WHERE
THIS LIGHT COMES FROM."

35:07.136 --> 35:09.608
AND THE BOY BLOWS OUT
THE CANDLE AND REPLIES,

35:09.608 --> 35:11.880
"IF YOU TELL ME
WHERE THIS LIGHT WENT,

35:11.880 --> 35:15.214
I'LL TELL YOU
WHERE IT COMES FROM."
CUTE.

35:15.214 --> 35:18.487
YOUR PARTNER IS RIGHT
ABOUT ONE THING--

35:18.487 --> 35:21.820
I COMMUNE WITH SOME
VERY DANGEROUS PEOPLE.

35:21.820 --> 35:24.793
I'M FRIENDS WITH THOSE
WILLING TO DON SUICIDE VESTS

35:24.793 --> 35:27.426
IN THE NAME OF IDEOLOGY.
I KNOW WHEN A MAN

35:27.426 --> 35:30.629
IS WILLING TO SACRIFICE
ANYTHING FOR HIS CAUSE,

35:30.629 --> 35:33.862
AND YOU'RE NOT THAT KIND
OF MAN, AGENT BENFORD.

35:33.862 --> 35:37.336
EVEN IF YOU WERE TO START
ASKING THE RIGHT QUESTIONS,

35:37.336 --> 35:40.469
YOU'RE NOT WILLING TO DO WHAT
IT TAKES TO GET THE ANSWERS.

35:40.469 --> 35:43.572
YOU'RE THAT LITTLE BOY,
AGENT BENFORD...

35:43.572 --> 35:45.714
ALONE IN THE DARK.

35:52.781 --> 35:55.684
(typing)

35:55.684 --> 35:58.927
(electronic whir)

35:58.927 --> 36:00.259
(taps button)

36:00.259 --> 36:03.262
(typing)

36:08.697 --> 36:10.199
(taps button, beep)

36:10.199 --> 36:11.840
(electronic dings)

36:14.773 --> 36:16.875
(Mark) HEY, AL.
(knocks on door)

36:16.875 --> 36:18.877
HEY, MAN.

36:20.509 --> 36:22.951
REMEMBER THAT HACKER--

36:22.951 --> 36:26.355
MR. CHEETO DUST?

36:26.355 --> 36:29.218
GIVE HIM A CALL.

36:30.859 --> 36:32.521
YOU SURE?

36:36.595 --> 36:38.597
YEAH.

36:41.199 --> 36:43.932
IT'S TIME WE GOT
OUT OF THE DARK.

36:53.211 --> 36:55.213
ADDISON'S DISEASE?

36:55.213 --> 36:56.885
WHO'S ADDISON?

36:56.885 --> 37:00.749
WELL, HE WAS THE GUY
WHO DISCOVERED THE CONDITION.

37:00.749 --> 37:03.992
IT'S A HORMONAL IMBALANCE THAT
MAKES SURGERY VERY DANGEROUS.

37:03.992 --> 37:06.925
BUT, UH, LUCKILY,
DR. BENFORD REALIZED IT IN TIME

37:06.925 --> 37:09.528
AND GAVE YOU THE MEDICATION
THAT SAVED YOUR LIFE.

37:09.528 --> 37:12.961
WOW. THANKS, DR. VARLEY.

37:12.961 --> 37:15.664
HEY, WE SHOULD THANK YOU.
(pager beeps)

37:15.664 --> 37:19.237
YOUR FLASH-FORWARDS
HELPED US PIECE IT TOGETHER.

37:19.237 --> 37:21.810
IF YOU HADN'T TOLD US
WHAT YOU SAW,

37:21.810 --> 37:24.473
YOU MIGHT HAVE DIED
ON THE TABLE.
IT'S PRETTY COOL.

37:24.473 --> 37:28.747
I WASN'T AFRAID, BECAUSE
I DIDN'T NEED TO BE AFRAID.

37:28.747 --> 37:32.020
THE FUTURE SAVED ME.

37:36.455 --> 37:40.559
UH, NED'S CRIT IS--
IS STABLE.

37:44.493 --> 37:46.495
LOOK, ABOUT EARLIER,
I, UM--

37:46.495 --> 37:48.497
I WAS COMPLETELY
OUT OF LINE.

37:48.497 --> 37:52.040
YEAH.
BUT YOU WERE ALSO RIGHT.

37:52.040 --> 37:55.704
I JUST DIDN'T WANT TO SEE
WHAT WAS GOING ON WITH NED

37:55.704 --> 37:59.478
'CAUSE OF WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH ME, SO...

37:59.478 --> 38:02.551
LOOK, I-I-I GET IT.
IT'S WHAT'S HAPPENING WITH ME.

38:02.551 --> 38:04.953
THAT'S WHAT
MADE ME BELIEVE HIM.

38:04.953 --> 38:07.956
MM-HMM.

38:07.956 --> 38:10.759
BRYCE, I HAVEN'T PUSHED YOU

38:10.759 --> 38:12.891
'CAUSE YOU DIDN'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT THE...

38:12.891 --> 38:15.924
(elevator bell dings)
ME STANDING ON THE PIER
WITH A GUN TO MY HEAD?

38:15.924 --> 38:17.866
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT I'M HERE

38:17.866 --> 38:20.699
IF YOU WANT TO TALK.

38:20.699 --> 38:24.873
THANKS, DR. B., BUT, UH,
I'M GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

38:24.873 --> 38:27.376
YOU REALLY THINK
YOU'RE JUST OKAY NOW?

38:27.376 --> 38:29.037
I KNOW I AM.

38:29.037 --> 38:32.511
THE FUTURE SAVED ME.

38:32.511 --> 38:35.514
(woman speaking indistinctly
over P.A.)

38:35.514 --> 38:37.346
OH, UH, DR. BENFORD?

38:37.346 --> 38:41.019
HEY.
I NEED YOU TO SIGN THE DISCHARGE
ON THE ROLLERBLADE GUY

38:41.019 --> 38:43.392
SO I CAN ROLL HIM
ON OUT OF HERE.
SURE.

38:43.392 --> 38:46.495
OH, AND DYLAN SIMCOE'S
WHITE COUNT SPIKED TO 19.

38:46.495 --> 38:49.758
HERE'S HIS C.V.C.
HE WAS TRANSFERRED
TO PHYSICAL THERAPY.

38:49.758 --> 38:52.861
CAN YOU GIVE IT
TO HIS ATTENDING?
THE CHIEF
TRANSFERRED HIM BACK.

38:52.861 --> 38:55.604
WHAT?
P.T.s SAID THEY COULDN'T
HANDLE THE ANTIBIOTICS,

38:55.604 --> 38:58.767
SO THE CHIEF PUT HIM
BACK ON YOUR SERVICE.

38:58.767 --> 39:01.840
ARE YOU OKAY, DR. BENFORD?

39:01.840 --> 39:04.643
YEAH. FINE.

39:04.643 --> 39:06.615
(door closes)

39:11.019 --> 39:13.552
HEY, NICOLE.

39:13.552 --> 39:14.883
(chuckles)

39:14.883 --> 39:17.426
UH, CHARLIE'S JUST UPSTAIRS
CHANGING INTO HER P.J.s.

39:17.426 --> 39:18.757
ALL RIGHT.

39:18.757 --> 39:20.589
UM, WE DID
SOME FINGER PAINTING,

39:20.589 --> 39:22.461
AND SHE'S ALL DONE
WITH HER HOMEWORK,

39:22.461 --> 39:25.434
AND, UH, WE KICKED AROUND
A SOCCER BALL, TOO.

39:25.434 --> 39:29.097
OH, AND SHE HAD ANTS ON A LOG
FOR A SNACK.
AND HOW ARE YOU DOING?

39:31.970 --> 39:34.473
I FEEL BAD FOR
DISAPPEARING ON YOU.

39:34.473 --> 39:37.446
EH, EVERYBODY DISAPPEARED
FOR A WHILE.

39:37.446 --> 39:40.709
SOME PEOPLE
AREN'T EVEN BACK YET.

39:40.709 --> 39:42.711
I GUESS I'M JUST
TRYING TO FIGURE OUT

39:42.711 --> 39:44.853
WHY YOU GUYS
DIDN'T FIRE ME.

39:44.853 --> 39:47.616
NICOLE,
YOU'RE PART OF THE FAMILY.

39:52.090 --> 39:54.092
HEY, WHAT'S THE MATTER?

39:54.092 --> 39:56.094
YOU WANT TO TALK
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED?

39:56.094 --> 39:58.096
YOU CAN, YOU KNOW.

40:02.701 --> 40:04.703
WHAT'S WRONG?

40:07.936 --> 40:10.939
I SAW SOMEONE DROWNING ME.

40:10.939 --> 40:12.611
WHAT?

40:12.611 --> 40:15.984
I SAW SOMEONE DROWNING ME...

40:15.984 --> 40:18.416
IN MY FLASH-FORWARD.

40:18.416 --> 40:23.452
(whoosh)
I SAW SOMEONE DROWNING ME,
AND I DON'T UNDERSTAND,

40:23.452 --> 40:26.555
BUT I-I FELT LIKE I DESERVED
WHAT WAS HAPPENING,

40:26.555 --> 40:30.959
LIKE I HAD DONE SOMETHING WRONG,
AND THERE'S NO OTHER WAY OUT.

40:30.959 --> 40:33.502
I SAW THE MAN'S FACE
WHO WAS DOING IT.

40:33.502 --> 40:36.134
HE PUSHED ME BACK DOWN,
AND...

40:36.134 --> 40:39.668
AND THEN I WAS JUST GONE.

40:39.668 --> 40:40.939
(whoosh)

40:40.939 --> 40:43.712
(voice breaking)
WHAT DID I DO

40:43.712 --> 40:45.974
THAT I THINK
I DESERVED GETTING KILLED?

40:45.974 --> 40:48.777
YOU DON'T KNOW EXACTLY WHAT
YOU SAW OR EVEN HOW YOU FELT.

40:48.777 --> 40:51.520
WHAT KIND OF PERSON DOESN'T
CARE THEY'RE BEING MURDERED?

40:51.520 --> 40:54.222
NICOLE,
I'VE KNOWN YOU A LONG TIME.

40:54.222 --> 40:57.526
YOU DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG,
AND YOU WON'T.

40:57.526 --> 41:00.028
TOMORROW I'M GONNA HAVE
A DETECTIVE FRIEND OF MINE

41:00.028 --> 41:01.890
FROM THE L.A.P.D.
COME TALK TO YOU.

41:01.890 --> 41:03.862
WE'RE NOT GONNA LET
ANYTHING BAD HAPPEN.

41:03.862 --> 41:07.596
I WANT TO DO WHATEVER I HAVE TO
TO MAKE SURE YOU'RE SAFE.

41:07.596 --> 41:09.167
ALL RIGHT?

41:09.167 --> 41:13.742
THAT PERSON
YOU THINK YOU SAW,

41:13.742 --> 41:16.174
THAT PERSON
YOU'RE WORRIED YOU MIGHT BE,

41:16.174 --> 41:18.907
THAT'S NOT YOU.

41:18.907 --> 41:22.881
DO YOU THINK YOU COULD
TRY TO BELIEVE THAT?

41:25.253 --> 41:27.916
YEAH. I CAN TRY.

41:27.916 --> 41:30.058
GOOD.

41:30.058 --> 41:33.892
(Charlie) HEY, DADDY.
HEY! COME HERE, YOU. OH!

41:33.892 --> 41:37.195
MOONS OVER MIAMI. YOU IN?
I'M IN.

41:37.195 --> 41:40.599
ALL RIGHT.
LET'S GET STARTED.
ARE YOU STAYING?

41:40.599 --> 41:43.001
UM, YOU KNOW WHAT?
I HAVE TO GO.

41:43.001 --> 41:45.003
SHE'S STAYING.
BREAKFAST FOR DINNER?

41:45.003 --> 41:48.577
CAN'T BEAT THAT.

41:48.577 --> 41:52.140
COME ON. PLEASE?
SOUNDS GREAT.

41:52.140 --> 41:55.013
GET CRACKING THE EGGS,
PROFESSOR.

41:55.013 --> 41:56.514
OKAY.

41:56.514 --> 41:59.287
CAN I HAVE A BOWL, PLEASE?
ONE BOWL COMING RIGHT UP.

41:59.287 --> 42:00.949
OKAY.
HERE.

