(laughs) THAT'S SILLY.
HERE WE GO. OKAY.

42:03.121 --> 42:04.723
(chuckles)

42:04.723 --> 42:07.996
GAMANTA, McGILLICUTTY...

42:07.996 --> 42:09.958
FROG LEG!
(gasps)

42:09.958 --> 42:11.960
DO YOU WANT THE COIN BACK?

42:11.960 --> 42:14.733
YEAH!
SAY THE MAGIC WORDS THEN.

42:14.733 --> 42:17.966
(Dylan) FROG LEG,
McGILLICUTTY...

42:17.966 --> 42:20.639
(Debbie) SEE YOU TOMORROW,
DR. BENFORD.
GOOD NIGHT, DEB.

42:20.639 --> 42:22.540
GAMANTA, McGILLICUTTY,

42:22.540 --> 42:24.773
FROG LEG.
THERE YOU GO.

42:24.773 --> 42:26.775
DO IT AGAIN!

42:26.775 --> 42:29.978
I THINK MY JUNIOR MAGICIAN
HAS TO GET HIS STRENGTH UP

42:29.978 --> 42:33.081
BEFORE THE NEXT TRICK.
HOW ABOUT SOME DINNER?

42:33.081 --> 42:36.554
OKAY, DAD.

42:39.257 --> 42:41.960
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

42:41.960 --> 42:44.763
UH, YOU'RE THE, UM,
THE EYE OF NEWT SOUP, RIGHT?

42:46.935 --> 42:49.267
ALL RIGHT. CHICKEN IT IS.

42:49.267 --> 42:52.671
(cell phone rings)

42:52.671 --> 42:54.643
(ring)

42:54.643 --> 42:55.974
(ring)

42:55.974 --> 42:57.906
(ring)

42:57.906 --> 42:59.147
(ring)

42:59.147 --> 43:00.679
YEAH?

43:00.679 --> 43:02.681
We need to talk.

43:02.681 --> 43:04.683
YEAH, WELL,
I CAN'T RIGHT NOW.

43:04.683 --> 43:07.055
Well, I'm truly sorry
about that, Lloyd,

43:07.055 --> 43:10.058
BUT TALKING TO ME IS JUST ONE
OF THOSE LITTLE INCONVENIENCES

43:10.058 --> 43:12.060
YOU'RE GOING
TO HAVE TO PUT UP WITH

43:12.060 --> 43:15.363
NOW THAT WE'RE RESPONSIBLE FOR
THE SINGLE GREATEST DISASTER

43:15.363 --> 43:17.365
IN HUMAN HISTORY.
